data.description: Welcome to this picturesque equestrian paradise! Nestled on 14.6 sprawling acres, this all brick home is a rural gem!  At the heart of this home is the inviting living room and family room adorned with hardwood floors, perfect for cozy evenings or entertaining. The formal dining room gives an elegant touch for gatherings. The apartment  over garage offers additional living space or potential rental income. A new roof and a new HVAC unit were added less than three years ago. This is a must see!
